sources.title: Teenage Catgirls In Heat 1994
sources.description: From IMDB: An Egyptian cat goddess in the form of a statuette commands all local felines to surrender one of their nine lives so they can transform into beautiful women to mate with (and terminate) human males, then prepare the way for "The Great Litter." A professional cat-tracker and a hitchhiker set out to stop them. --- Surprisingly well shot movie despite the abysmal quality of this rip. There is a bit of a plot and the movie is generally good natured. Sure, the cats are killing people but they are cute and play with yarn.
